<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Apr 2022 10:41:41 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>【評測】AVIOT TE-D01gs 無線耳機，日系靚聲、細粒輕量、多色選擇、CP 值高</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/08/aviot-te-d01gs-review/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=aviot-te-d01gs-review</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 08 Apr 2022 10:24:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[aptX]]></category><category><![CDATA[耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[藍牙耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[降噪]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1094589</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>市面上貴價藍牙耳機都賣到接近甚至超過 2 千元，不過如果想簡簡單單幾百元貨色，而又想要靚聲，其實都有好選擇。在 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>市面上貴價藍牙耳機都賣到接近甚至超過 2 千元，不過如果想簡簡單單幾百元貨色，而又想要靚聲，其實都有好選擇。在日本多次獲得當地音響耳機獎項的品牌 AVIOT，旗下就有一個超平價產品線，這次介紹的 AVIOT TE-D01gs，有多色選擇而機身輕盈，適合輕度用家，最重要是這樣的價錢，仍能走到靚聲路線，調音完全日系，聽開流行曲的用家可以一試。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0001.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0001-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0003-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0003-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0003-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0003-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0003-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>多色設計機身輕盈</h2><p>今次小編就集齊了 AVIOT TE-D01gs 所有顏色，包括了白色、黑色、紅色、藍色、橙色共 5 款顏色。每一隻顏色都採用透明充電盒，你甚至可隱約看到裡面的電池，這款透明外殼採霧面光滑平面設計，讓它有幾分貴氣。充電盒大小就有如一個小打火機，充電盒上蓋有磁石黏合盒身，穩固之餘也顯出這款入門耳機不簡單。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0004.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0004-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0005-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0006.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0006-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0006-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0006-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0006.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0007.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0007-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0007-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0007-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0008-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0008-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0008-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0008-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0008-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0011.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0011-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0011-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0011-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0011.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>入門耳機功能齊全</h2><p>AVIOT TE-D01gs 耳機雖然不算是極端細粒，但每邊耳機重量只為 4.6g，相當輕巧，長期佩戴也不會造成負擔。這款入門級耳機不設主動降噪，不過靠佩戴舒適感以及合適耳朵的耳塞，都可做到不錯的隔音效果。左右耳機都有實體按鈕操作播放、歌曲跳躍等，適合不喜歡輕觸操作的用家。留意耳機不設除下感應器，除下耳機要放入充電盒，才能中斷跟手機或裝置的連結。耳機設有位置記錄功能，配合手機應用程式，能記下最後放置的位置，讓你忘記耳機到底放了在家中還是在 Office，心裡都有一個譜。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0014.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094872" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0014-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0014-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0014-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0022.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0022-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0022-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0022-768x467.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳機採用高感度咪高風，語音通話時自己的聲音清晰，不會有多餘噪音甚至迴響聲混入，適合講電話或者參與視像會議之用。</p><h2>入門機但支援 aptX 編碼，日系調音音色啱口味</h2><p>小編認為這款入門耳機重點在於，以這個價錢提供不錯的音色。雖然耳機價位屬入門級，但就支援 aptX 編碼格式。小編在 DAP 手提播放器或 Android 手機上連接此耳機，音樂分析度、音色豐富程度可進一步提高。而對於一個 6mm 動圈單元來說，耳機已經實現了它的最好音質，可見 AVIOT 的調音特質特別適合亞洲歌曲，迎合亞洲人口味，也就是在低頻、中頻、高頻的清晰度都顧及的同時，展現出下潛感適中、有衝擊力度而並非淡如白紙的重低音效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0023-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094874" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0023-1-694x440.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0023-1-694x440.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0023-1-768x487.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0023-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0024.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0024-694x426.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="426" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0024-694x426.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0024-768x472.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0024.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外耳機中頻清晰度高，令人聲部份得以展現出在這個價位的耳機中，比較高清晰力的表現，尤其是母音（A,I,U,E,O) 發聲清晰得來圓滑。不過有時耳機始終中頻開放感頗強，有時會有例外聽得出少許毛刺感，或像大聲公般中頻突然太突出的感覺，但也是可接受範圍。</p><p>以下個別歌曲測試以 MOOV 為測試平臺，連接 Google Pixel 4a 智能手機並以 aptX 編碼方式連接。</p><p>收聽 Kendy Shen《日月無常》24bit 48kHz FLAC，此曲的電子音樂中呈現出圓滑的女聲。歌曲可聽到女聲與背景搖滾樂背景有一個清晰的分離，音響迴響十足，而低頻、敲擊電子樂器的下潛感適中，配合 aptX 連接清晰度會比好多同價位耳機為佳。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_-922x2048.jpg 922w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-51-45-026_com.now_.moov_.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>收聽姜濤《Dear My Friend,》24bit 48kHz FLAC，歌詞能夠非常清晰地閱讀，同時歌曲開首鋼琴與背景效果音的迴響廣闊，而入到主歌部份的重低音表現醇厚有力度。歌曲整體以歌手的歌聲為主導，距離感相當近。再回到 solo 的清唱部份，同樣展現出耳機音場的迴響力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_-922x2048.jpg 922w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-03-447_com.now_.moov_.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a></p><p>收聽 Anson Lo《Mr Stranger》24bit 48kHz FLAC，可體會到有力度與下潛感的低頻打擊，同時男聲以及中高頻的電子樂器可從音樂中分離出來清晰聽到，音樂迴響感不錯，這對耳機你不會聽到有潛水的閉塞感覺。音色表現會以音樂、人聲清晰為大前提，再配以中等至較強勁的低頻，聽上去不會被閉塞的低音不舒服或耳痛。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_-922x2048.jpg 922w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-24-775_com.now_.moov_.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a></p><p>而除了流行音樂之外，小編也對其他智能手機常聽種類的音源作出測試。</p><p>ASMR 音源：雖然耳機的低頻能力並非頂尖，但仍聽到有力的戳耳反應，耳機較適合收聽如雨聲、風聲等中頻至高頻分析力需求高的音效</p><p>YouTube 清淡節目、直播：耳機突出的中頻令直播主聲音極為清晰，整體以中頻為主導，聲音延遲低</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube-922x2048.jpg 922w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Screenshot_2022-04-08-16-52-58-232_com.google.android.youtube.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a></p><h2>手機 App 可自行調校 EQ 等化器</h2><p>上面的測試在不調整 EQ 等化器的情況下進行。用戶可在手機安裝專用 App，裡面可輕微調節低頻、中頻、高頻的表現幅度，在這對三頻平衡的耳機上，相對其他同類耳機，較容易找到適合你的音色。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/螢幕截圖-2022-04-08-17.25.20.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094902" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/螢幕截圖-2022-04-08-17.25.20-587x580.jpg" alt="" width="587" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/螢幕截圖-2022-04-08-17.25.20-587x580.jpg 587w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/螢幕截圖-2022-04-08-17.25.20-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/螢幕截圖-2022-04-08-17.25.20-768x759.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/螢幕截圖-2022-04-08-17.25.20.jpg 810w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 587px" /></a>▲（左）耳機專用手機 App 可記錄耳機最後出現的地方 （右）專用 App 可調節 EQ 等化器，微調個人化音色</p><h2>總結：簡簡單單，但有齊想要的功能與音色</h2><p>如果你買耳機的預算有限，但想有音質較好的耳機，可以一試 AVIOT TE-D01gs。耳機機身與充電盒物料看似十分廉價，設計師以顏色與拋光霧面的設計令它外觀看上去依然不錯。而它的 6mm 動圈單元雖然簡單，但廠商在調音以及 aptX 編碼的支援，令它發揮盡了它應有的音樂分析能力，在這個價位來說，已令人相當滿意。有感此耳機彷彿像把各種入門級的材料，烹調到一碟味道不錯的菜色。耳機適合收聽以人聲為主、純音樂等，要求中頻、中高頻分析力的歌曲，有興趣的朋友可試聽為實。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0019.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094893" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0019-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0019-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0019-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/unwire0019.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
